    "English": "Compressed Atmospheric Gas",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "压缩大气气体",
    "TencentChinese": "压缩大气气体",
    "TraditionalChinese": "大氣壓縮氣體"
  },
  "Description": {
    "English": "A reactive atmospheric <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">gas</span> found wherever there is organic life.<br><br>Nitrogen is readily harvested from the atmospheres of <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">Lush</span> and <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">Toxic</span> planets.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一种在只要有有机生命的任何地方都能找到的活性大气<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">气体</span>。<br><br>氮很容易从<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">茂盛</span>和<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">有毒</span>星球的大气中收获。",
    "TencentChinese": "一种在只要有有机生命的任何地方都能找到的活性大气<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">气体</span>。<br><br>氮很容易从<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">茂盛</span>和<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">有毒</span>星球的大气中收获。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "有機生命居住之處必可找到的活性大氣<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">氣體</span>。<br><br>氮可從<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">茂盛</span>與<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">劇毒</span>的星球大氣中直接採收獲得。"
  },
