    "TraditionalChinese": "加工氮"
  },
  "PinObjectiveTip": {
    "English": "<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">Nitrogen</span> is a reactive atmospheric <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">gas</span> found wherever there is organic life.<br>With the aid of an <span class=\"name name-technology\">Atmosphere Harvester</span>, can be extracted from the atmospheres of <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">Lush</span> and <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">Toxic</span> planets.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">氮</span>是一种在只要有有机生命的任何地方都能找到的活性大气<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">气体</span>。<br>可以使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">大气采集器</span>，从<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">茂盛</span>和<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">有毒</span>球上的大气中将气体提取出来。",
    "TencentChinese": "<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">氮</span>是一种在只要有有机生命的任何地方都能找到的活性大气<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">气体</span>。<br>可以使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">大气采集器</span>，从<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">茂盛</span>和<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">有毒</span>球上的大气中将气体提取出来。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">氮</span>是只要有有機生命之處就可見活性大氣<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">氣體</span>。<br>若借助<span class=\"name name-technology\">大氣採集器</span>，可從<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">茂盛</span>和<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">劇毒</span>星球的大氣層中萃取到。"
  },
  "PinObjectiveMessage": {
    "English": "Deploy an <span class=\"name name-technology\">Atmosphere Harvester</span> on <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">lush</span> and <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">toxic</span> worlds",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "在<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">繁茂</span>和<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">毒性</span>星球部署一台<span class=\"name name-technology\">大气收集器</span>",
    "TraditionalChinese": "在<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">茂盛</span>或<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">劇毒</span>世界部署<span class=\"name name-technology\">大氣採集器</span>"
  },
